parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, leading to loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The power steering warning light illuminates
the steering wheel becomes stiff or difficult to turn
the radio turns on and off
and the vehicle may stall or experience a sudden loss of power steering assist.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, leading to loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The power steering warning light illuminates intermittently
the steering wheel becomes stiff or difficult to turn intermittently
and the vehicle may experience a sudden loss of power steering assist.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering pump can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, leading to loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The power steering warning light illuminates
the steering wheel becomes stiff or difficult to turn
and the vehicle may experience a sudden loss of power steering assist.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, compromising the safety of the vehicle's occupants.
symptoms: Airbags fail to deploy in a crash
airbag warning light remains on
airbag sensor malfunctions
airbag inflators may not deploy properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a malfunction in the airbag system, potentially leading to airbag deployment failure in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Airbag warning light remains on
airbag sensor malfunctions
airbag inflators may not deploy properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of Takata airbag inflators can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, compromising the safety of the vehicle's occupants.
symptoms: Airbag inflators may not deploy properly
airbag warning light remains on
airbag sensor malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping or downshifting issues can cause the vehicle to jerk or hesitate, leading to loss of control, accidents, or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission shifts independently into third gear
the vehicle jerks violently
the transmission indicator illuminates
the vehicle idles rough
the transmission slips or downshifts unexpectedly
the vehicle's brakes become less effective.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch master cylinder can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission control module can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to unexpected shifting, loss of power, or complete failure of the transmission.
symptoms: The transmission control module fails
the transmission shifts independently
the vehicle's engine light illuminates
the transmission indicator illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the neutral safety switch can cause the vehicle to start in gear, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle starts in gear
the vehicle will not start in park
the vehicle starts in neutral.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The powertrain/carrier and pinion issues can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to unexpected shifting, loss of power, or complete failure of the transmission.
symptoms: Grinding noise from the transmission
the transmission slips or downshifts unexpectedly
the vehicle's engine light illuminates.
